This is broadly true.

body:
It has been said that the devil has all the best tunes.

This is broadly true.

But heaven has the best choreographers.

***

I just started reading this book and… 🥰🥰🥰

I wanted Aziraphale to look like the physical embodiment of being handed a warm mug of hot cocoa, while Crowley looks like a mix between a CEO and a goth college-aged girl. I feel like a achieved that.

They’re dancing to “Good Old Fashioned Lover Boy,” if you must know.

❤️
